H. Peter Anvin wrote:
> This is indeed very cool :)  Does it support handling the telephone
> interface (hangup, ring detect, etc) as well?  If so, it could be used
> as an answering machine, if nothing else :)
It currently handles detecting dial tone, busy tone, and a few other
things, using the on board DSP.  Dialing and hangup are done properly.
It is not quite ready to be an answering machine, but nearly.
Full tone detection, ring detection and so on is coming soon.
-- Jamie
